Five years and more than 100,000 copies after
it was first published, it's hard to imagine
anyone working in Web design who hasn't read
Steve Krug's "instant classic" on Web usability,
but people are still discovering it every day.
In this second edition, Steve adds three new
chapters in the same style as the original:
wry and entertaining,
